/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fd05bf2b465add8f3aabfb24303f62676aca7e","tid":422504,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"880469b79823f214f52bbe46f3dd8b80ef6e4b20","tid":422504,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72db00dd45b1558de53d1bd8872498bafd551586","tid":422504,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"究竟有幾多次警已報係真有其事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n化膠水幫到你呀樓主，效果同哥羅芳一樣"},{"pid":"9effe9cb7346ed6ae6fe1a88d7907ec1566a8e81","tid":422504,"uid":71954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用少少白膠漿都 ok，乾左會變透明</blockquote><br />\n試過唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能因為整箱<br />\n如果整板可能都得<br />\nBtw thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個箱幾大<br />\n細野通常化膠水都痴到<br />\n但痴得靚好考手工<br />\n<br />\n如果你有 fd 識 lasercut ，可以整啲凹凸接口<br />\n再入筍，喺啲接口位落膠水"},{"pid":"d2d299990b9f98ff610f1018d5519bfe64a2b9bd","tid":422504,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"好似化寶桶燒屍個post"}]}